Class CrimeAvailabilityMethodCall

  • java.lang.Object
    • police.methodcalls.BaseMethodCall
      • police.methodcalls.CrimeAvailabilityMethodCall

  • public class CrimeAvailabilityMethodCall
extends BaseMethodCall
    Encapsulates the following Police API methods:
    • crimes-street-dates: Lists dates for which data is available.
    • crime-last-updated: Retrieves the last date on which the crime information was updated.

    filip
